              "text": "Everything that Christ accomplished"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Is for all God’s children meant."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As His child you are included,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For His word stands fast and true;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "So by faith you now inherit"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "All that He has done for you."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Did you know God has a family?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Yes, He does, in fact, it’s us."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That’s why we are here enjoying"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "All He is, so marvelous."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He’s our God and we’re His people,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Day by day we love Him more;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We’re so happy and so thankful,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We just praise Him o’er and o’er."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "All we know is that we love Him,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We’re so glad for what He’s done;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We are brought to Him, and we all"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Know the joy of being one."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We’re so glad that we’re included,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "What a fellowship have we!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "So we’d like to welcome you, friend,"
            }
